title: Ep. - 246 - EXECUTIVE PRODUCER OF THE MASKED SINGER
description:
Izzie Pick Ibarra is the Executive Producer of The Masked Singer on Fox. She talks about bringing Dancing With the Stars to the United States, creating Ladies of London on Bravo, and how the team at Fox is able to keep the identities of The Masked Singer contestants so secret.

 

 

Reality Life with Kate Casey
